{"title":"红河水向南流","authors":["梁上泉"],"dates":[{"year":1963,"month":11,"day":7}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"红河水向南流"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梁上泉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红河水，向南流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流出红河三角洲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"波涛滚滚入南海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海水汹涌向金瓯；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金瓯半岛到十七度线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"线分越南成两半，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两半个国土两半个天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北边明亮南边暗；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"暗无天日夜漫漫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这么大个监狱还少见，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田野飞跳着鹰和犬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"囚徒一千四百万！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千百万颗心儿向北方，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"渴望统一胜思乡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冲破黑牢迎旭日，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丛林里举起刀和枪；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枪口对枪口刀对刀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生成的竹子气节高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"制成矛柄和旗竿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"竿头的大旗不停地飘；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飘过平原飘过山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飘过溪流飘过川，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"川上听得见红河的浪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山头望得见河内的烟；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烟云浪声在召唤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"誓把祖国连一片，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“战略村”变“战斗村”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不让“毒蜻蜓”空中转！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要得解放靠斗争，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真理的太阳已东升，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"豪情付与血和火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"化为阳光照春莺。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}